OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early patchy light rain
OL,6,Fwill soon clear to leave a generally
OL,7,Fdry and bright day, with some sunny
OL,8,Fspells developing later. Temperatures
OL,9,Fslightly lower than previous days.
OL,10,FWinds generally light.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FDry with variable, often
OL,13,Flarge, amounts of cloud but also clear
OL,14,Fspells. Temperatures will fall
OL,15,Fslightly lower compared to Friday
OL,16,Fnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
