OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FMainly dry with often large
OL,6,Famounts of cloud, but some bright or
OL,7,Fsunny spells. Light onshore winds will
OL,8,Fkeep coastal areas cooler, also bring
OL,9,Fthe chance of patchy low cloud.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,12,FPredominantly dry and becoming very
OL,13,Fwarm or hot, with the heat peaking
OL,14,FTuesday. Chance occasional mist or low
OL,15,Fcloud along the coast. Humid and very
OL,16,Fwarm nights.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
